1
00:00:34,180 --> 00:00:35,940
=The Embroidered Truth=

2
00:00:44,640 --> 00:00:48,479
Charged with murder and jailbreak,

3
00:00:48,600 --> 00:00:51,960
yet you appear before me.

4
00:00:52,840 --> 00:00:56,359
You want to make a deal, don't you?

5
00:00:56,439 --> 00:00:58,640
Jia Yi deserved to die.

6
00:00:58,840 --> 00:01:00,880
Who killed him doesn't matter.

7
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:05,079
What matters is who can
help you rise, Your Honor.

8
00:01:06,239 --> 00:01:08,680
Am I right?

9
00:01:14,840 --> 00:01:18,719
Then what do you want me to do?

10
00:01:25,959 --> 00:01:27,799
Here's where the murder
weapon is hidden.

11
00:01:27,840 --> 00:01:28,959
I only need you

12
00:01:29,319 --> 00:01:31,400
to present it to the
Princess Consort yourself.

13
00:01:35,159 --> 00:01:36,359
Anyone else,

14
00:01:36,599 --> 00:01:38,000
and I'd hesitate.

15
00:01:38,599 --> 00:01:39,760
But Wu Lian?

16
00:01:41,280 --> 00:01:42,680
I'll do it.

17
00:01:47,940 --> 00:01:50,380
(Yanyu Embroidery House,
Wu Lian's studio, Scholar's shelf)

18
00:01:50,460 --> 00:01:54,380
=Episode 14=

19
00:01:55,359 --> 00:01:57,480
How's your hand?

20
00:01:57,640 --> 00:02:02,640
Not great, but I can still
embroider with my left.

21
00:02:03,079 --> 00:02:04,120
It's slower,

22
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:05,920
but if I work day and night,

23
00:02:06,239 --> 00:02:07,959
I'll make the Flower Festival.

24
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:11,120
The gown is very important.

25
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:14,039
Be careful with your hand.

26
00:02:14,159 --> 00:02:15,400
Thank you for your concern,
Your Highness.

27
00:02:16,159 --> 00:02:18,000
Though the city's been chaotic,

28
00:02:18,599 --> 00:02:20,439
I've been working day and night.

29
00:02:20,639 --> 00:02:21,800
Rest assured,

30
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:22,759
Your Highness.

31
00:02:25,439 --> 00:02:26,400
Your Highness.

32
00:02:26,439 --> 00:02:27,080
Xiaotao...

33
00:02:27,080 --> 00:02:28,199
Xiaotao is missing.

34
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,560
Wang Lu reports

35
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:32,120
that Lady Cheng'en is surely involved.

36
00:02:32,280 --> 00:02:33,439
Hung from the city gate,

37
00:02:33,439 --> 00:02:35,000
could she just fly away?

38
00:02:35,479 --> 00:02:35,879
Go.

39
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:37,199
Send people to investigate.

40
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:38,039
Yes.

41
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:42,960
Seems I'll need

42
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:45,879
more guards at my embroidery house.

43
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:50,759
I have an idea. Seal off the city.

44
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:52,639
Catch all these thieves

45
00:02:52,639 --> 00:02:54,080
and hand them to the prefect.

46
00:02:54,479 --> 00:02:56,319
Stop the panic.

47
00:02:59,639 --> 00:03:01,560
Things are indeed unstable.

48
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:04,520
But sealing the city needs
too many soldiers.

49
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:07,879
People will think something
terrible happened.

50
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:11,120
I only meant to teach Ruoheng a lesson.

51
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:12,719
No need for a big fuss.

52
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:15,599
The Prince returns any day now.

53
00:03:15,599 --> 00:03:17,000
If this blows up,

54
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:19,560
it'll embarrass everyone.

55
00:03:20,199 --> 00:03:21,800
Well said, Your Highness.

56
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:24,680
Master Wu, if you're concerned,

57
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:27,280
bring a few trusted embroiderers

58
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:29,439
and stay at the manor.

59
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,759
The Flower Festival is near.

60
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:34,120
Welcoming the Prince is what matters.

61
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:36,000
Yes.

62
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:37,719
How is Xiaotao's injury?

63
00:03:39,159 --> 00:03:40,479
She's out of danger.

64
00:03:40,479 --> 00:03:41,479
Just needs rest.

65
00:03:49,080 --> 00:03:50,000
Miss Rulan,

66
00:03:50,479 --> 00:03:51,800
Wu Lian moved into the manor.

67
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:54,719
Officers are everywhere.

68
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:56,800
They're parading Feng Da's body.

69
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:59,759
They have sketches of your face
and are searching door to door.

70
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:03,199
Wu Lian fears we might act,

71
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:05,120
so he's hiding in the manor.

72
00:04:05,439 --> 00:04:06,719
The Princess Consort is desperate
to find you,

73
00:04:06,879 --> 00:04:08,960
only to avoid trouble
at the Flower Festival.

74
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,039
No.

75
00:04:12,199 --> 00:04:13,000
I must return to the manor.

76
00:04:13,159 --> 00:04:13,719
No!

77
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:15,719
That's walking into the lion's den.

78
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:16,879
Besides, the Princess Consort...

79
00:04:16,879 --> 00:04:17,839
As long as I'm useful to her,

80
00:04:17,839 --> 00:04:19,319
that's enough.

81
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:21,560
News just came.

82
00:04:25,380 --> 00:04:28,100
(To win the Prince back,
cut the phoenix.)

83
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:29,360
What's wrong?

84
00:04:31,199 --> 00:04:33,759
I have to go back to the manor.

85
00:04:34,439 --> 00:04:37,439
There are some things only I can do.

86
00:04:41,399 --> 00:04:42,240
(Ruoheng,)

87
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:43,920
(though I'm not certain,)

88
00:04:44,240 --> 00:04:45,800
(with your help from afar,)

89
00:04:45,959 --> 00:04:47,120
(even if it's the gates of hell,)

90
00:04:47,199 --> 00:04:48,920
(I will barge through them.)

91
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:51,120
Since ancient times,

92
00:04:51,279 --> 00:04:53,639
the finishing touch is
the most important step.

93
00:04:54,199 --> 00:04:58,199
I used to burn incense and bathe
before doing it.

94
00:04:58,439 --> 00:05:00,120
But since we're at the manor,

95
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:03,160
I'd like to invite you to do the honors.

96
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:07,360
Add unique elegance to this gown.

97
00:05:09,759 --> 00:05:10,519
My Lady, please stop.

98
00:05:10,519 --> 00:05:11,160
Move!

99
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:15,519
See who's making noise.

100
00:05:15,639 --> 00:05:16,120
How dare you!

101
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:18,920
You dare block my way?

102
00:05:33,639 --> 00:05:34,959
I'm seeing my cousin.

103
00:05:35,079 --> 00:05:36,120
Who dares stop me?

104
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:45,079
I trust Magistrate Yu

105
00:05:45,279 --> 00:05:47,800
has already found proof
of Lady Cheng'en's innocence.

106
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:49,519
The prison is full of bones,

107
00:05:49,959 --> 00:05:51,079
filthy and unbearable.

108
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:53,000
No place for me.

109
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:55,519
You come and go as you please.

110
00:05:56,040 --> 00:05:57,959
A death row can't hold you.

111
00:05:59,399 --> 00:06:01,959
I missed you so much in jail, Wenyue,

112
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:03,319
so I came to see you.

113
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:04,920
Seeing you well,

114
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:06,319
I can rest easy.

115
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:08,160
I just want to know

116
00:06:08,439 --> 00:06:10,600
when my name will be cleared.

117
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:11,519
Ruoheng,

118
00:06:12,279 --> 00:06:15,000
Magistrate Yu will decide.

119
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:18,000
Wenyue, you still don't trust me.

120
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:19,720
I came all this way for you.

121
00:06:20,639 --> 00:06:23,279
I thought you were just punishing me.

122
00:06:23,759 --> 00:06:27,160
I didn't think
you'd side with that wretch

123
00:06:27,279 --> 00:06:28,600
to kill me.

124
00:06:30,079 --> 00:06:30,879
Fine.

125
00:06:31,639 --> 00:06:33,199
I'll go back to death row.

126
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:36,319
The rest is up to you, Wenyue.

127
00:06:36,639 --> 00:06:37,439
Ruoheng!

128
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:41,519
Didn't death row teach you any humility?

129
00:06:41,839 --> 00:06:43,879
Will you act like this when the Prince

130
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:45,360
comes back?

131
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:55,120
The authorities are hunting us.

132
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:56,839
Anyone who goes out will die.

133
00:06:57,439 --> 00:06:58,399
I'm not afraid to die.

134
00:06:58,839 --> 00:06:59,639
Calm down.

135
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:01,759
We're not afraid to die,

136
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:03,920
but aren't you afraid of
troubling Rulan?

137
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:07,120
If Rulan returns to the manor,

138
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:08,839
she'll clear our names.

139
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:11,639
Then we can truly help her.

140
00:07:13,079 --> 00:07:13,839
So in the end,

141
00:07:13,839 --> 00:07:14,879
all we can do is wait.

142
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:17,600
Ruoheng,

143
00:07:18,439 --> 00:07:21,000
it's because I believe you're innocent

144
00:07:21,399 --> 00:07:23,360
that I let Magistrate Yu act justly.

145
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:25,839
But your childish temper...

146
00:07:26,079 --> 00:07:28,319
One small upset,
and all hell breaks loose.

147
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:31,560
I think it's time you grew up.

148
00:07:33,959 --> 00:07:35,839
Wenyue, I know I was wrong.

149
00:07:36,079 --> 00:07:37,560
I broke out of jail

150
00:07:37,639 --> 00:07:39,000
because I didn't want to be wronged.

151
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:41,920
I feared bringing disaster to the manor.

152
00:07:42,199 --> 00:07:45,000
Wenyue, I've already explained
to Magistrate Yu.

153
00:07:45,199 --> 00:07:46,600
He's waiting outside.

154
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:48,240
He can prove my innocence.

155
00:07:48,399 --> 00:07:49,879
I really didn't kill anyone.

156
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:54,000
Since Your Highness and Lady Cheng'en
haven't seen each other,

157
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:55,759
I'll take my leave.

158
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:57,600
Wait.

159
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:03,560
Your Highness,

160
00:08:03,879 --> 00:08:05,680
after a thorough investigation,

161
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:07,199
Lady Cheng'en is innocent.

162
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:09,000
Magistrate Yu, you are diligent.

163
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:10,680
If Lady Cheng'en is innocent,

164
00:08:10,879 --> 00:08:14,399
then was all that evidence false?

165
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:16,240
Your Highness,

166
00:08:16,399 --> 00:08:19,680
the evidence was incomplete.
It was my oversight.

167
00:08:19,759 --> 00:08:22,680
I found the real murder weapon.

168
00:08:22,680 --> 00:08:25,240
It proves Lady Cheng'en's innocence.

169
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:28,160
Witnesses can lie.

170
00:08:28,279 --> 00:08:29,480
They don't count.

171
00:08:29,639 --> 00:08:32,879
But a weapon is solid proof.

172
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:36,399
Present the weapon.

173
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:44,120
Your Highness,

174
00:08:44,399 --> 00:08:48,000
this knife was used by guards
at Yanyu Embroidery House.

175
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:51,600
(Wu)
It's engraved with the character "Wu."

176
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:54,000
Knives like this

177
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:57,000
can be forged by any blacksmith
in Jinxiu City.

178
00:08:59,399 --> 00:09:03,000
Then find the real killer

179
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:04,799
and clear Ruoheng's name.

180
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:06,000
Your Highness,

181
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:07,080
there is another suspect.

182
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:10,519
I must take him in for questioning.

183
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:11,399
Who?

184
00:09:14,639 --> 00:09:15,799
Master Wu.

185
00:09:18,480 --> 00:09:20,080
How could it be Master Wu?

186
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:23,960
The weapon was found in
Wu Lian's bedroom.

187
00:09:24,679 --> 00:09:27,039
Your Highness, I'm an embroiderer.

188
00:09:27,039 --> 00:09:28,399
What use would I have for a knife?

189
00:09:28,639 --> 00:09:30,559
Someone is trying to frame me!

190
00:09:30,799 --> 00:09:31,960
Please see the truth!

191
00:09:32,039 --> 00:09:33,519
Magistrate Yu has solved
countless cases.

192
00:09:33,639 --> 00:09:34,440
He must have his reasons.

193
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:35,200
Your Highness,

194
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:36,679
I have something to say.

195
00:09:36,799 --> 00:09:37,879
The evidence is right here.

196
00:09:37,960 --> 00:09:39,080
How dare you lie?

197
00:09:39,559 --> 00:09:40,360
Ruoheng!

198
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:17,040
♪Night fades before the dawn♪

199
00:10:17,280 --> 00:10:20,280
♪Old vows still guide my hand♪

200
00:10:21,480 --> 00:10:24,240
♪The past no longer binds♪

201
00:10:24,720 --> 00:10:28,440
♪My heart still shines through dust♪

202
00:10:28,880 --> 00:10:33,000
♪Silent blooms, unchanged heart♪

203
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:36,720
♪Bare hands weave through the frost♪

204
00:10:37,080 --> 00:10:39,080
♪Shadows linger, rain returns♪

205
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:43,160
♪Honor crowns my weary soul♪

206
00:10:43,560 --> 00:10:45,760
♪For your faith that never broke♪

207
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:50,080
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

208
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:52,880
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

209
00:10:52,880 --> 00:10:57,120
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

210
00:10:58,320 --> 00:11:00,800
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

211
00:11:00,920 --> 00:11:03,560
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

212
00:11:03,560 --> 00:11:06,160
♪One thought turns into ash♪

213
00:11:07,120 --> 00:11:12,480
♪No future left to write♪

214
00:11:13,560 --> 00:11:15,360
♪If I never fall♪

215
00:11:15,400 --> 00:11:17,760
♪How could this waiting end♪

216
00:11:17,760 --> 00:11:19,120
♪If I bear no scars♪

217
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:21,440
♪How could I challenge fate♪

218
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:23,800
♪I knew there was no way back♪

219
00:11:23,800 --> 00:11:27,800
♪Yet I left this hope behind♪

220
00:11:27,920 --> 00:11:30,040
♪For your faith that never broke♪

221
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:34,200
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

222
00:11:35,160 --> 00:11:37,080
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

223
00:11:37,080 --> 00:11:41,480
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

224
00:11:42,560 --> 00:11:45,160
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

225
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:47,760
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

226
00:11:47,760 --> 00:11:50,120
♪One thought turns into ash♪

227
00:11:51,240 --> 00:11:56,480
♪No future left to write♪

228
00:11:57,360 --> 00:11:59,760
♪The lamp is out, you're gone♪

229
00:12:01,040 --> 00:12:03,160
♪Heaven and earth fall silent♪

230
00:12:04,840 --> 00:12:07,040
♪If we meet again someday♪

231
00:12:07,480 --> 00:12:13,280
♪This longing sleeps beneath the snow♪
